<s> OK, so I haven't read every piece of mail on this list ... Can someone answer this simple question: If I make a request for a page with a Cookie header, is the result cacheable in a public cache ?  </s>
<s> e.g.  </s>
<s> I pick up a cookie with path=/ from some org, then get a GIF (which has no Set-Cookie, Expires now, Cache-control, etc.), can it be cached ?  </s>
<s> I think I had misunderstood the mechanism somewhat; if I want to use the cookie in a page, should I make that page uncacheable with Expires, Cache-Control, etc. ??  </s>
<s> Andrew  </s>
<s> Microsoft's proxy caches responses from requests with cookie headers if no cache-control / Expires / pragma: no-cache / etc. is present in the response.  </s>
<s> We've been operating this way since October and have seen no problems with it... Vinod Valloppillil  </s>
